---
title: Enoki Mushroom and Udon Noodle Stir Fry with Green Beans and Carrots
description: Enoki mushrooms are popular in Japanese cuisine. These little fungi look different depending on how they grow—in the wild, they are brown in colour, but when cultivated without light exposure, they become white.
